Good health is the balance between body, mind & soul. We have seen too many cases, how they are interconnected and intertwined and affect each other. We need to be agile, if one of the aspects is out of balance it would impact our overall health. We've seen this during Covid, how important mental health is. The lockdown has taught several things. One of them is how difficult life can get when indoors. This has been a learning experience for me and in this journey, @chinmayee.tammareddy Ji presence had helped me a lot with her expertise in emotional intelligence.

What an honour to meet celebrated Bollywood and Netflix star Manisha Koirala earlier this month!
 
It was inspiring to see Manisha chat about her experience of ovarian cancer with Ovacome members Samixa and Preeti and a privilege to inform her about the work we do to support the ovarian cancer community and reduce health inequalities.
 
Thank you Manisha for taking the time to come to visit us.
 
If you’d like to support our work, please consider making a donation via our website, or requesting symptom awareness packs to raise awareness in your local community. 

👉Visit the link in our bio to read our full blog post and to view the full video. 

#ovariancancer #cancerawareness #cancersupport #cancercharity

🌿 Nature Walk: A Soulful Escape into the Wild 🌳

This morning was all about reconnecting with nature and embracing the healing power of the great outdoors. Forest bathing, or shinrin-yoku, isn’t just a walk in the woods—it’s a mindful journey that awakens the senses.

The rustling leaves, birdsong, and fresh earthy aroma felt like a gentle reset for the mind and soul. Each step reminded me of how nature holds space for us, offering peace and perspective.

If you’re looking for a way to unwind, breathe deeply, and recharge, a nature walk might just be the remedy you need. 🌸

When was the last time you let nature work its magic on you? 🌿✨

#ForestBathing #NatureWalk #MindfulnessInNature #HealingWithNature

📸 @saroshpradhan

2024 has been a wonderful year, so many memories, so much of success and so much inspiration, all from @m_koirala mam❤️✨
She’s been a beacon of hope & strength to many of us. @m_koirala mam has taught us that there’s always light at the end of any dark tunnel. 

From all the way in South Africa I just want to say thank you @m_koirala mam, for all that you are, for being your beautiful true self and what makes you beautiful is your personality and the love and appreciation you have for those that appreciate you and shower you with love!❤️… I started of this fanpage without any hope, but here you are appreciating me being here, it’s enough to last a lifetime for me✨❤️

I have so much love and admiration for you @m_koirala mam❤️.. you are a true superhero and you made us all proud❤️.. your portrayal of Mallikajaan won so many hearts & her character will live in our hearts forever❤️✨

May 2025 bring you more love, light, happiness & success. We as your fans will stand with you till eternity! Love you very much Manisha mam❤️✨

2024: The Year of Manisha Ma'am's Triumphant Return!
 Oh, what a year it has been for our beloved Manisha Ma'am! From the grand success of Heeramandi to the prestigious Filmfare Awards, Asian Academy Creative Awards, and ITA Awards, Ma'am has been shining brighter than ever!

As a die-hard fan, I'm beyond thrilled to see Ma'am receiving the recognition she deserves. Her hard work, dedication, and passion for her craft are truly inspiring, and I'm so grateful to have her as a role model in my life.

That's why I decided to start this fan page - to celebrate Ma'am's success, share her remarkable journey, and spread love and positivity to all the fellow fans out there!

Manisha Ma'am, you're not just an actress; you're a symbol of hope, resilience, and determination. Your eyes sparkle with a fire that ignites our souls, and your performances leave us awestruck and inspired!

To Ma'am and all the amazing fans out there, let's keep shining, keep celebrating, and keep spreading love! Here's to many more years of Ma'am's success, talent, and inspiration!! 🙏🏻❤️
